 the university of kashmir and an mba from new york university transactions date shares transaction value     gift at  per share      gift at  per share      gift at  per share      gift at  per share      derivativenonderivative trans at  per share      derivativenonderivative trans at  per share      derivativenonderivative trans at  per share      derivativenonderivative trans at  per share      derivativenonderivative trans at  per share      derivativenonderivative trans at  per share      gift at  per share                gift at  per share      gift at  per share      gift at  per share      gift at  per share      gift at  per share      gift at  per share      gift at  per share      gift at  per share      gift at  per share      gift at  per share      disposition at  per share      disposition at  per share      disposition at  per share      disposition at  per share      gift at  per share      gift at  per share      disposition at  per share  copyright  factset research systems inc all rights reserved source factset fundamentals officers and executives mr m farooq kathwari chairman president  chief executive officer mr corey whitely cfo treasurer  executive vpadministration mr clifford thorn vice presidentupholstery manufacturing mr philip greenwald vice presidentreal estate mr daniel m grow senior vice presidentbusiness development ms tracy paccione vice presidentmerchandising mr henry c kapteina senior directorinternal audit mr john s bedford chief accounting officer vp  controller ms november rawlings managerpublic relations mr eric d koster secretary vice president  general counsel ms tara i stacom independent director mr domenick j esposito independent director mr john j dooner lead independent director ms mary a garrett independent director mr james b carlson independent director dr james w schmotter independent director trending tickers quoteszigmancomposite vuzi quoteszigmancomposite jcp quoteszigmancomposite nugt quoteszigmancomposite tlt qu