veral organizations worth magazine recognition of one of  best ceo’s in usa the national retail federation gold medal recipient of the international first freedom award from the council for america’s first freedom ernst  young’s entrepreneur of the year award and the antidefamation league’s humanitarian award in  kathwari became cochair of the muslimjewish advisory council an organization founded to address antimuslim and antijewish bigotry in the united states personal lifeedit kathwari is of kashmiri descent hailing from srinagar his father went to lahore pakistan in  for a short business trip and found himself stranded as the authorities in srinagar cancelled his return permit he settled in pakistan and assumed an official role in the azad kashmir government in  farooq along with his mother and siblings moved to pakistan to join his father the family lived in pakistan for  years they returned to kashmir in  whence kathwari spent a few years in college and participated as an activist in the kashmiri political movement he was to return to pakistan again in  a week before the indopakistani war broke out there he obtained his travel documents to finally migrate to the united states referencesedit  jayne odonnell june   ceo profile ethan allens kathwari was always a leader usa today retrieved feb     a b susan berfield oct   at ethan allen selling furniture and tolerance businessweek archived from the original on    american born son of ethan allen furniture tycoon farooq kathwari was killed fighting jihad in afghanistan  trump effect jewish and muslim organizations form new alliance  us election  haaretz retrieved november     ethan allen’s chief in fight of his life  a b farooq kathwari speech at lahore university of management sciences retrieved from httpsenwikipediaorgwindexphptitlefarooqkathwarioldid categories living peopleamerican muslimsamerican people of kashmiri descentpeople from new rochelle new yorkindian emigrants to pakistanpakistani emigrants to the un